# My API

Built with [Rapina](https://rapina.rs) v0.11.0.

## Routes

### POST /v1/users

Request (application/json):
```json
{
  "properties": {
    "email": {
      "type": "string"
    }
  },
  "type": "object"
}
```

Response:
```json
{
  "properties": {
    "id": {
      "type": "number"
    }
  },
  "type": "object"
}
```

Errors:
  - 409 CONFLICT: email already registered
